headline: Convert YouTube JSON to TSV
description:
Example usage:

(1.sh search utility and yy059 are described in earlier submissions)

   1.sh search_query > 1.yts
   yy059 < 1.yts|1.sh >> 1.yts
   yy059 < 1.yts|1.sh >> 1.yts
   1.sh /c/channelname > 1.ytc
   yy059 < 1.ytc|1.sh >> 1.ytc
   cat 1.yt[sc]|yy062 > 1.tsv
   less -SN 1.tsv
   1.sh $(sed -n 1000p 1.tsv|cut -f3) >> 1.tsv
This is made for me and thus only includes the columns I want. I am often selecting videos based on running length.
